\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Today I want to look at a passage of scripture that is ridiculous in my opinion.  If you have a Bible open it to Joshua 10\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 7\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So Joshua marched up from Gilgal with his entire army,\'a0including all the best fighting men.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is so important this verse here\'85what does Joshua do?  He marches. \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 8\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The\'a0Lord\'a0said to Joshua, \'93Do not be afraid\'a0of them; I have given them into your hand.\'a0Not one of them will be able to withstand you.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Wouldn\'92t it be awesome if God said something like that to you today?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is what I don\'92t know\'85I don\'92t know your problem, I don\'92t know your plan, but I know your God\'85and here\'92s the secret that shouldn\'92t be a secret but we keep forgetting it like it is
\f0\b\fs28 \'85You\'92ve already won!\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf5 \super 9\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub After an all-night march from Gilgal, Joshua took them by surprise.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I NEED to pause right here\'85he marched all night.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There was urgency in his path.  He didn\'92t drag his feet\'85he didn\'92t wait till morning.  (I can sit here for a while if I need to)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 10\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The\'a0Lord\'a0threw them into confusion\'a0before Israel,\'a0so Joshua and the Israelites defeated them completely at Gibeon.\'a0Israel pursued them along the road going up to Beth Horon\'a0and cut them down all the way to Azekah\'a0and Makkedah.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 11\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub As they fled before Israel on the road down from Beth Horon to Azekah, the\'a0Lord\'a0hurled large hailstones\'a0down on them,\'a0and more of them died from the hail than were killed by the swords of the Israelites.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That is a crazy story\'85a story where God took the effort of man and combined it with his power and did something amazing.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They couldn\'92t have won the battle without God, God wouldn\'92t have done it without their effort!\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
