\ls11\ilvl0
\f4\b\fs28 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}3 things I want to point out here:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was incorrect\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I hear people say all the time, I don\'92t know how to pray.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What he asked for didn\'92t even make sense to us does it?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is looking at your heart and knows what you need more than you do.  Just ask!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God knows you and what you need and isn\'92t interested if it is the correct prayer\'85he knows you and your situation and what is coming down the pipeline better than you do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What he is looking for are people who dependent upon Him, not theologically correct in everything they say.  \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl2
\f4\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can even be cleaning a bathroom and pray\'85there is not a right or wrong way.  It\'92s about your heart not your head!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Quit letting insecurity talk you out of talking to God!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1
\f3\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is was ridiculous\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you imagine during the speech what his soldiers thought\'85they were probably with him until that moment and then all of sudden I have to believe more than a few were a little confused!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was so large that it was impossible without God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The size of your prayers to God are a reflection of the size your relationship with God.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was public\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the craziest one in my opinion.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s easy to dream privately isn\'92t it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To pray big prayers that no one hears and so when/if they don\'92t come true we are ok.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We just sort of move on quickly.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
